======================================================================
KEY OBSERVATIONS
======================================================================

  1. H_{odd}(T_7, T_7\v) = [0, 0, 0]
     All <= 1? True

  2. H_{even}(T_7, T_7\v) = [0, 7, 0]
     Any > 1? True

  3. This confirms the ODD/EVEN DICHOTOMY:
     H_{odd}(T, T\v) <= 1 => beta_{odd} <= 1 (Boolean)
     H_{even}(T, T\v) can be large => beta_{even} can be large
